{"tid":2501623,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過食炸薯條之類的野一下子食太多太快 口腔會無啦啦自己含膿發炎? (症狀可能過幾個鐘後會自己消退)","createTime":"2021-04-23T13:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T14:44:51.000Z","uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"177b09dfb0083d5a2b353696c6699488833c0aae","tid":2501623,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:32:29.000Z","msg":"發炎位置會濃血紅色 或者黑色燶咗咁<br />\n位置通常口腔兩側 或者係口腔上顎接近喉嚨位置<br />\n<br />\n利申: 好小心 絕對無咬親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2001e46bd30fb2e4ad3d7afc8ff56803a89dfbe","tid":2501623,"uid":49592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"係咪 黑色一 tat 咁??"},{"pid":"b587a2a5e60eb817be6d184ba2ef25fafb101d78","tid":2501623,"uid":310125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"試過 一個禮拜好返"},{"pid":"ee6d68f32676022213353ab28b8f166f207d5192","tid":2501623,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:00:33.000Z","msg":"損左 有時一下食太多好熱既野都會咁"},{"pid":"7113581eb8b15f7eed8d44d0f7d3d414aa5fa652","tid":2501623,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2001e46bd30fb2e4ad3d7afc8ff56803a89dfbe","tid":2501623,"uid":49592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"係咪 黑色一 tat 咁??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"係呀 燶咗咁 仲會隆起"},{"pid":"7a1e855b1da9000322d3d44adc52395bf60e1554","tid":2501623,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"有 唔洗淆 我仲未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f3da8f58561f02b54bdf518859def15bd87790","tid":25